author: peterjones
msg: CXF-117  Fix for wsdl validation with imported wsdls/xsds.
The validators shouldn't choke on valid wsdl which happens to use schema
types imported from another wsdl or xsd file.
Added test for validating a wsdl which includes a wsdl.
Added test for validating a wsdl which includes an xsd.
Fixed some typos in error messages.
Anyone familiar with the validators please feel free to review and comment.
